<div style="color:#990000;font-size:x-large;font-weight:900">
Static Analysis for Groovy: Less Bugs, Better Code
</div>

<p>
  <strong>CodeNarc</strong> analyzes Groovy code for defects, bad practices, inconsistencies, style issues
    and more. A flexible framework for rules, rulesets and custom rules means it's easy to configure CodeNarc
    to fit into your project. Build tool, framework support, and report generation are all enterprise ready.
</p>


